<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Hello World!</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper-sidebar"></div>
    <div class="wrapper-content">
      <div class="content-title"><h1>Hello World!</h1></div>
      <div class="content-body">
        <p>This is a containerized Node.js application on OpenShift Container Platform for IBM Z!</p>
        <p>This app allows you to view and add to a sample database of user data, being stored in MongoDB.</p>
        <div class="wrapper-form">
          <div class="form-newuser"><p>If this is your first time using the app, start by adding a new user below:</p>
          <form id="formNewUser" name="newuser" method="get" action="/newuser">
            <button id="btnSubmit" type="submit">Add a New User</button>
          </form></div>
          <div class="form-userlist"><p>If you've previously added users and want to view your userlist, click below:</p>
          <form id="formUserlist" name="Userlist" method="get" action="/Userlist">
            <button id="btnSubmit" type="submit">View Userlist</button>
          </form></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
